        "name": "Mesh convergence and GCI study for CFD hemolysis model",
        "description": "Systematic mesh refinement study performed using the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry at the 5.0 L/min / 3600 RPM operating point. GCI computed per Celik et al. (2008) methodology.",
        "startedAtTime": "2023-03-01T09:00:00Z",
