      "rationale": "The observational registry covered 47 procedures with continuous telemetry, encompassing all 5 COU operating points within the convex hull of observed conditions. Blood analogue fluid properties (viscosity, density) matched COU specification within 3 %. Temperature maintained at 37 ± 1 °C consistent with normothermic CPB. Gradation 2 satisfied."
